Enum NumberFormat.Style

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<NumberFormat.Style>
      • java.text.NumberFormat.Style

    NumberFormat
    public static enum NumberFormat.Style
extends Enum<NumberFormat.Style>
    A number format style.

    Style is an enum which represents the style for formatting a number within a given NumberFormat instance.

    Since:
    12
    See Also:
    CompactNumberFormat, NumberFormat.getCompactNumberInstance(Locale, Style)
